Blocks the current thread until the cell is initialized.

# Example

Waiting for a computation on another thread to finish:
```rust
use std::thread;
use std::sync::OnceLock;

let value = OnceLock::new();

thread::scope(|s| {
    s.spawn(|| value.set(1 + 1));

    let result = value.wait();
    assert_eq!(result, &2);
})
```
